name: Ina'nis: Tako Rescue Mission
description:
A Hololive fan game featuring Hololive EN's Ninomae Ina'nis.

Play through 5 + 1 platformer levels to rescue the captured Takodachi.

***************************************************

CONTROLS:

Attack (Close Range) - Z

Attack (Long Range)/Grapple - X

Pause - C

Movement - Arrow Keys

Full Screen Toggle - Space Bar
